00:30:21,380 --> 00:30:22,580
(Little Bro)

566
00:30:22,580 --> 00:30:23,660
(Calling)

567
00:30:32,190 --> 00:30:33,230
Hello, what's up?

568
00:30:33,670 --> 00:30:34,390
Chen Huan'er.

569
00:30:35,040 --> 00:30:36,300
Some tricks you've got there.

570
00:30:36,760 --> 00:30:37,780
Leniency for confession,

571
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:39,000
resisting authoritarianism.

572
00:30:39,150 --> 00:30:39,670
Tell me.

573
00:30:40,390 --> 00:30:42,300
Where did you get so many tickets from?

574
00:30:42,820 --> 00:30:44,100
I got them from Coach Li.

575
00:30:45,990 --> 00:30:47,390
Pay attention to your steps!

576
00:30:47,390 --> 00:30:48,540
Faster, faster!

577
00:30:50,430 --> 00:30:51,190
What are you doing?

578
00:30:51,780 --> 00:30:52,780
Watch your step!

579
00:30:53,710 --> 00:30:54,580
Hello, sir.

580
00:30:54,950 --> 00:30:56,580
The tickets for Sunday's finals.

581
00:30:56,630 --> 00:30:58,020
Can I have one?

582
00:30:58,190 --> 00:30:58,990
Sure. Help yourself.

583
00:31:01,300 --> 00:31:02,470
Next. Hurry up!

584
00:31:02,470 --> 00:31:03,150
Thanks.

585
00:31:05,300 --> 00:31:06,540
I'm taking three.

586
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:09,910
Hey, are you listening?

587
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:11,460
Did you not eat breakfast this morning?

588
00:31:11,460 --> 00:31:12,150
It was that easy?

589
00:31:12,360 --> 00:31:13,260
What did you think?

590
00:31:13,260 --> 00:31:14,820
Did you think I had to beg on my knees

591
00:31:14,820 --> 00:31:15,990
just to get the tickets?

592
00:31:20,230 --> 00:31:20,780
Okay.

593
00:31:21,150 --> 00:31:22,190
Never mind, just asking.

594
00:31:22,470 --> 00:31:23,580
That's all. Bye.

595
00:31:36,190 --> 00:31:37,340
Take it slow. Be careful.

596
00:31:37,390 --> 00:31:38,060
I'm fine, Mom.

597
00:31:38,060 --> 00:31:39,260
I'm almost fully recovered.

598
00:31:40,100 --> 00:31:41,670
Good morning, Aunt Lin.

599
00:31:41,870 --> 00:31:43,060
Morning, Huan'er.

600
00:31:43,340 --> 00:31:45,300
Jing Xichi, I'll take you today.

601
00:31:46,500 --> 00:31:47,950
Didn't Song say he'd take me?

602
00:31:48,020 --> 00:31:50,120
The teacher asked him
to go for a competition.

603
00:31:50,820 --> 00:31:54,060
Why don't I call a cab for you guys?

604
00:31:55,260 --> 00:31:56,820
It's okay. We can get there on the bike.

605
00:31:56,840 --> 00:31:58,220
You're going to be late for work.

606
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:59,190
Don't worry about us.

607
00:31:59,230 --> 00:32:00,400
Okay, I'm going to be late.

608
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,340
I'll leave him to you.

609
00:32:01,340 --> 00:32:02,240
You guys figure it out.

610
00:32:02,240 --> 00:32:02,820
I'll handle it.

611
00:32:02,820 --> 00:32:03,320
Thank you.

612
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:04,060
Got it.

613
00:32:04,060 --> 00:32:05,140
Call a cab if you need to.

614
00:32:05,180 --> 00:32:05,900
Don't worry.

615
00:32:07,950 --> 00:32:09,670
Come on, get on.

616
00:32:11,390 --> 00:32:12,710
You added a cushion for me?

617
00:32:12,870 --> 00:32:13,540
That's right.

618
00:32:14,430 --> 00:32:15,500
Aren't I considerate?

619
00:32:15,540 --> 00:32:16,920
Don't want your butt to bruise.

620
00:32:17,060 --> 00:32:17,780
Come on then.

621
00:32:19,990 --> 00:32:21,580
Are you sure you can do it?

622
00:32:21,740 --> 00:32:22,710
Why not?

623
00:32:22,780 --> 00:32:24,100
Just get on and see.

624
00:32:24,390 --> 00:32:25,390
Give me your bag then.

625
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:28,300
No biggie. I can still ride
with the bag.

626
00:32:28,390 --> 00:32:29,390
I'm going to get on.

627
00:32:29,470 --> 00:32:29,820
Go on.

628
00:32:31,230 --> 00:32:31,990
Here, take a seat.

629
00:32:32,630 --> 00:32:33,430
Sit tight.

630
00:32:33,580 --> 00:32:34,060
Here I go.

631
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:34,740
Hang on.

632
00:32:34,780 --> 00:32:35,580
Okay, go ahead.

633
00:32:35,670 --> 00:32:36,540
I'm going to go fast.

634
00:32:36,670 --> 00:32:37,780
Not too fast, please.

635
00:32:38,540 --> 00:32:40,260
My leg just healed.

636
00:32:47,990 --> 00:32:48,580
Are you tired?

637
00:32:50,300 --> 00:32:51,060
No.

638
00:32:51,430 --> 00:32:52,390
This is nothing.

639
00:32:53,740 --> 00:32:54,340
Chen Huan'er.

640
00:32:55,230 --> 00:32:57,060
Even though you added
such an ugly backseat

641
00:32:57,150 --> 00:32:58,780
to my beloved bike,

642
00:32:59,580 --> 00:33:00,670
I'm actually pretty touched.

643
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:03,780
But at this speed,

644
00:33:03,780 --> 00:33:05,390
when are we ever going to get to school?

645
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:07,950
Well, you could take a taxi.

646
00:33:07,990 --> 00:33:08,910
No.

647
00:33:09,230 --> 00:33:10,630
I'm a disabled man.

648
00:33:10,780 --> 00:33:11,820
Even if I'm late,

649
00:33:11,950 --> 00:33:13,060
I have a legitimate excuse.

650
00:33:13,190 --> 00:33:14,820
But I don't, bro.

651
00:33:16,020 --> 00:33:16,740
Exactly.

652
00:33:16,820 --> 00:33:18,150
So you better hurry up and push,

653
00:33:18,230 --> 00:33:19,640
or you're going to get punished.

654
00:33:20,180 --> 00:33:21,100
Don't just stand there.

655
00:33:21,150 --> 00:33:21,710
Push!

656
00:33:21,820 --> 00:33:22,260
I...

657
00:33:22,500 --> 00:33:23,910
Let's go! Hurry up!

658
00:33:24,080 --> 00:33:25,120
Ugh, you're so annoying.

659
00:33:25,120 --> 00:33:26,230
Careful! Don't make me fall.

660
00:33:26,470 --> 00:33:26,780
Faster.

661
00:33:45,390 --> 00:33:46,780
(That morning on the way to school,)

662
00:33:46,870 --> 00:33:48,480
(I don't even know how long it took.)

663
00:33:48,740 --> 00:33:51,260
(And even though he says
everything's back to normal,)

664
00:33:51,870 --> 00:33:53,190
(I could tell.)

665
00:33:53,780 --> 00:33:55,470
(His recovery)

666
00:33:55,780 --> 00:33:58,500
(is dragging out
much longer than any before.)

667
00:34:28,180 --> 00:34:29,470
(But Jing Xichi would never)

668
00:34:29,500 --> 00:34:30,870
(say something cheesy like,)

669
00:34:30,950 --> 00:34:33,580
("Pain is what makes youth real.")

670
00:34:33,910 --> 00:34:35,350
(He'd just scoff,)

671
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,270
(call it dramatic,)

672
00:34:36,540 --> 00:34:37,790
(and get right back to it.)

673
00:34:53,390 --> 00:34:55,310
Look here, Jing Xichi.

674
00:34:55,430 --> 00:34:56,180
Look here.

675
00:34:57,660 --> 00:34:58,220
What?

676
00:34:58,350 --> 00:35:01,220
Mountain pose. My dad taught me.

677
00:35:03,500 --> 00:35:04,580
Stop kicking.

678
00:35:04,620 --> 00:35:06,270
Your leg has only just healed.

679
00:35:07,390 --> 00:35:08,350
You have no idea

680
00:35:08,430 --> 00:35:09,060
how many rounds

681
00:35:09,060 --> 00:35:11,430
my heart's been flying on the field.

682
00:35:12,060 --> 00:35:13,990
Anyway, the physical therapist said

683
00:35:14,020 --> 00:35:15,220
that I'm recovering well.

684
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:17,990
He said I could try out for the upcoming
special training recruitment.

685
00:35:18,620 --> 00:35:19,350
You have no clue

686
00:35:19,430 --> 00:35:20,580
how much I miss the smell

687
00:35:20,660 --> 00:35:21,620
of the lawn.

688
00:35:24,020 --> 00:35:24,790
Lawn?

689
00:35:25,870 --> 00:35:27,870
You miss the smell of grass?

690
00:35:28,180 --> 00:35:28,990
Okay.

691
00:35:29,430 --> 00:35:30,540
I'll satisfy your wish.

692
00:35:30,580 --> 00:35:31,660
You miss grass, right?

693
00:35:31,790 --> 00:35:32,620
Here, have a whiff.

694
00:35:32,910 --> 00:35:34,310
I know you know the smell of grass.

695
00:35:34,350 --> 00:35:35,430
It's prickling my face!

696
00:35:35,470 --> 00:35:36,320
Doesn't it smell good?

697
00:35:36,340 --> 00:35:36,870
Chen Huan'er!

698
00:35:36,990 --> 00:35:37,750
Don't you like it?

699
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,580
I don't like this.

700
00:35:38,620 --> 00:35:39,860
I want a lawn, not just grass!

701
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:40,500
Why get me this?

702
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:41,310
It's nice!

703
00:35:41,310 --> 00:35:41,980
You like it, huh?

704
00:35:41,980 --> 00:35:43,000
I'll end up with allergies.

705
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:43,600
You like it.

706
00:35:43,600 --> 00:35:44,320
I don't want this.

707
00:35:44,350 --> 00:35:45,270
I know you like it.

708
00:36:09,180 --> 00:36:09,660
Hello?

709
00:36:10,430 --> 00:36:10,990
Hi.

710
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:11,910
The orthopedic book

711
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:13,350
you asked for last time has arrived.

712
00:36:13,500 --> 00:36:14,950
You can pick it up when you're free.

713
00:36:16,430 --> 00:36:16,990
Thanks.

714
00:36:17,240 --> 00:36:18,430
I'll come get it tomorrow.

715
00:36:53,390 --> 00:36:54,100
You're here.

716
00:36:54,220 --> 00:36:54,750
Hey,

717
00:36:55,020 --> 00:36:56,220
the book I ordered...

718
00:37:01,910 --> 00:37:02,390
Here.

719
00:37:02,910 --> 00:37:04,750
Thanks. It's 150, right?

720
00:37:05,750 --> 00:37:06,430
180.

721
00:37:08,140 --> 00:37:09,180
Wasn't it 150?

722
00:37:10,580 --> 00:37:11,990
This book is out of print.

723
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:14,240
I had to check with
multiple publishers to find it,

724
00:37:14,300 --> 00:37:16,100
so there's a markup.

725
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:18,800
Then why didn't you
mention that over the phone?

726
00:37:18,820 --> 00:37:19,860
Do you want it or not?

727
00:37:27,830 --> 00:37:29,790
I didn't bring enough money.

728
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:31,140
Can I pay you the rest next time?

729
00:37:35,060 --> 00:37:35,830
I'll cover it.

730
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:43,540
This, too.

731
00:37:46,350 --> 00:37:47,540
Just pay me back later.

732
00:37:49,140 --> 00:37:49,700
Thanks.

733
00:37:50,920 --> 00:37:52,340
You're here to buy books too?

734
00:37:54,580 --> 00:37:56,620
Math in our second year
has gotten a lot harder,

735
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:58,830
so I bought two extra
exercise books to practice.

736
00:37:59,990 --> 00:38:02,350
I heard that after
you transferred to the art class,

737
00:38:02,380 --> 00:38:03,880
you've been studying really hard.

738
00:38:03,950 --> 00:38:04,470
If you ever

739
00:38:04,470 --> 00:38:05,540
need help with anything...

740
00:38:05,540 --> 00:38:06,140
Song Cong,

741
00:38:07,350 --> 00:38:08,790
is studying

742
00:38:08,870 --> 00:38:10,430
the only thing in your life?

743
00:38:13,420 --> 00:38:15,430
I just wanted to thank you
for helping me earlier.

744
00:38:15,700 --> 00:38:17,790
I know. You don't want
to owe me a favor, right?

745
00:38:36,620 --> 00:38:38,350
Every time before I go to tutoring,

746
00:38:38,790 --> 00:38:40,180
I would come here for a bit.

747
00:38:42,380 --> 00:38:44,640
Actually, back when
I was taking TOEFL classes,

748
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:46,240
I used to skip them and come here too.

749
00:38:47,430 --> 00:38:48,580
You? Skipping class?

750
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:51,870
Why wouldn't I?

751
00:38:57,270 --> 00:38:58,830
Everyone thinks I'm too perfect.

752
00:39:00,270 --> 00:39:01,620
Even Xichi and Huan'er do.

753
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:04,700
What's up with you three?

754
00:39:06,470 --> 00:39:07,310
Nothing.

755
00:39:07,910 --> 00:39:08,830
Everything's fine.

756
00:39:13,180 --> 00:39:14,020
Honestly,

757
00:39:14,620 --> 00:39:16,320
I think there's still
some misunderstanding

758
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,060
between you guys.

759
00:39:21,830 --> 00:39:23,180
Last time, I said some things

760
00:39:23,750 --> 00:39:25,020
that were a bit too much.

761
00:39:27,620 --> 00:39:29,020
I thought about it afterward.

762
00:39:30,990 --> 00:39:32,990
I realized it was just me
being too stubborn.

763
00:39:34,140 --> 00:39:37,020
My family's housekeeper told me before.

764
00:39:37,420 --> 00:39:39,100
My problem is that I never say anything.

765
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:41,470
I get it.

766
00:39:41,800 --> 00:39:44,140
Maybe if I just talked about it,
everything would be fine.

767
00:39:45,830 --> 00:39:47,180
But I just can't get the words out.

768
00:39:53,790 --> 00:39:54,870
Actually, I'm the same way.

769
00:39:58,300 --> 00:39:59,790
Do you remember when you asked me

770
00:39:59,790 --> 00:40:01,310
why I thought your essays were good?

771
00:40:02,950 --> 00:40:04,020
It's because

772
00:40:05,910 --> 00:40:08,060
you always manage to express things

773
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:10,270
that I don't know how to put into words.

774
00:40:13,870 --> 00:40:14,990
Then do you know why

775
00:40:14,990 --> 00:40:15,950
I just told you

776
00:40:15,950 --> 00:40:17,320
all those things from my heart?

777
00:40:19,350 --> 00:40:20,060
Why?

778
00:40:23,470 --> 00:40:24,540
Because I like you.

779
00:40:28,660 --> 00:40:29,500
What did you say?

780
00:40:32,310 --> 00:40:33,180
I said...

781
00:40:33,700 --> 00:40:35,700
I will become someone as amazing as you.

782
00:40:55,470 --> 00:40:56,060
Huan'er.

783
00:40:56,950 --> 00:40:57,660
Aunt Lin.

784
00:40:57,790 --> 00:40:58,270
Here,

785
00:40:58,790 --> 00:41:00,350
have some water. It's hot, isn't it?

786
00:41:00,500 --> 00:41:01,270
Not too bad.

787
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:03,100
There are quite a lot of people today.

788
00:41:04,620 --> 00:41:06,540
By the way, isn't Uncle Jing coming?

789
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,020
He's on duty today.

790
00:41:08,350 --> 00:41:10,220
He'll come over
as soon as his shift ends.

791
00:41:14,750 --> 00:41:15,750
Coach Li is over there.

792
00:41:16,350 --> 00:41:17,020
I'll go ask him

793
00:41:17,020 --> 00:41:18,310
about today's recruitment.

794
00:41:18,870 --> 00:41:19,470
Alright.

795
00:41:29,990 --> 00:41:31,660
Here, drink some water.

796
00:41:32,100 --> 00:41:32,620
Thanks.

797
00:41:48,140 --> 00:41:49,910
Give me your hand.

798
00:41:50,580 --> 00:41:51,140
What for?

799
00:41:53,180 --> 00:41:54,140
My mom made me

800
00:41:54,140 --> 00:41:55,870
wear this red string since I was little.

801
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:58,580
Consider it me sharing
some of my luck with you.

802
00:42:00,220 --> 00:42:01,750
It should help a bit, right?

803
00:42:09,100 --> 00:42:10,310
Are you really giving me

804
00:42:10,660 --> 00:42:11,580
something so important?

805
00:42:12,870 --> 00:42:13,870
It's not a gift,

806
00:42:14,140 --> 00:42:15,540
just a temporary loan.

807
00:42:15,790 --> 00:42:16,470
If you like it,

808
00:42:16,500 --> 00:42:17,940
I'll make you another one later.

809
00:42:23,220 --> 00:42:23,870
Thanks.

810
00:42:26,470 --> 00:42:27,620
But don't worry.

811
00:42:29,020 --> 00:42:30,390
Now that I'm back in the game,

812
00:42:30,660 --> 00:42:32,020
I'm going to dominate the field.

813
00:42:32,140 --> 00:42:34,440
Of course! You're my Big Brother Jing!

814
00:42:58,840 --> 00:43:04,010
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

815
00:43:05,800 --> 00:43:10,880
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

816
00:43:12,650 --> 00:43:18,000
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

817
00:43:18,310 --> 00:43:23,800
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

818
00:43:26,390 --> 00:43:31,410
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

819
00:43:33,200 --> 00:43:38,440
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

820
00:43:40,040 --> 00:43:45,460
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

821
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:51,420
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

822
00:43:52,620 --> 00:43:56,580
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

823
00:43:56,580 --> 00:44:01,570
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

824
00:44:01,700 --> 00:44:05,130
♪And full of life♪

825
00:44:06,420 --> 00:44:09,880
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

826
00:44:09,880 --> 00:44:14,990
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

827
00:44:15,250 --> 00:44:19,640
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

828
00:44:20,140 --> 00:44:24,040
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

829
00:44:24,040 --> 00:44:28,980
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

830
00:44:28,980 --> 00:44:31,770
♪To know right from wrong♪

831
00:44:33,680 --> 00:44:37,210
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

832
00:44:37,210 --> 00:44:40,460
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

833
00:44:40,620 --> 00:44:46,380
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

834
00:44:46,800 --> 00:44:51,400
♪At just the right time♪
